WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.720
Instead of sitting in bed rotting all day,

00:00:01.721 --> 00:00:05.841
I suggest going to a park and sitting on a bench and rotting.

00:00:05.842 --> 00:00:07.721
Because at least A.

00:00:07.722 --> 00:00:09.961
You have reason to shower and get out of bed and get dressed,

00:00:09.962 --> 00:00:12.321
and B. You get a little bit of fresh air,

00:00:12.322 --> 00:00:14.601
nature, and like you can doom scroll on your phone.

00:00:14.602 --> 00:00:15.521
If you need to do that,

00:00:15.522 --> 00:00:17.841
do it. But maybe outside.

00:00:17.842 --> 00:00:19.561
That is the extent of the suggestions I have.

00:00:19.562 --> 00:00:20.581
I'm still on my phone,

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:21.553
but at least I'm in a park.
